A vintage-style illustration depicting a medieval round table scene reimagined with modern elements: armored knights gathered around a circular wooden table, but instead of swords and shields, they're passing glowing source code scrolls between each other. The table has a large open treasure chest at its center overflowing with interconnected gears, circuit patterns, and flowing ribbons of light representing shared knowledge. The knights wear a mix of chainmail and subtle modern accessories like glasses. The color palette features warm sepia tones, aged parchment textures, and golden highlights. The scene is lit by candlelight mixed with soft digital glows emanating from the scrolls. The composition suggests collaboration, sharing, and a noble purpose, with an arched stone chamber backdrop featuring banners showing abstract symbols of community and freedom.
